                  , on the <rs id="t18300114-7-cd39" type="crimeDate">23rd of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-7-off38 t18300114-7-cd39"></join>, at St. 
                     <persName id="t18300114-7-person171">
                        Mary 
                        Abbotts
